description:
Karolina Muchova and Beatriz Haddad Maia are scheduled to play each other in a quarterfinal matchup in the US Open Women’s Singles Tournament on September 4, 2024.

This market will resolve to “Muchova” if Karolina Muchova wins her match against Beatriz Haddad Maia in the quarterfinals of the US Open Women’s Singles tournament.

This market will resolve to “Haddad Maia” if Beatriz Haddad Maia wins her match against Karolina Muchova in the quarterfinals of the US Open Women’s Singles tournament.

If the match ends in a tie, is canceled, or delayed beyond September 11, 2024, this market will resolve to 50-50.

The primary resolution source for this market will be official information from the US Open (ex: https://www.usopen.org/index.html) including live footage, however a consensus of credible reporting may also be used.
